# Artifacts

<!-- This file tracks registered deliverable artifacts and their
     truth key dependencies. Each artifact is an H2 heading with
     the relative path from the deal folder root, followed by a
     fenced YAML code block with metadata.

     Format:

     ## deliverables/retention/retention_analysis_v9.docx
     ```yaml
     workstream: "retention"
     registered: "2026-03-22"
     last_refreshed: "2026-03-22"
     references:
       - "customer_253_mrr"
       - "t12m_cohort"
       - "t12m_retained"
       - "ndr_pct"
     scanner_findings:
       - "revenue_growth_yoy"
       - "gross_margin_pct"
     notes: ""
     ```

     Fields:
       workstream    - workstream this artifact belongs to
       registered    - ISO 8601 date when artifact was first registered
       last_refreshed - ISO 8601 date of last refresh (artifact regenerated)
       references    - list of truth keys this artifact depends on
       scanner_findings - keys found by scanner but not confirmed by analyst
       notes         - free-text notes

     Paths use forward slashes on all platforms.

     This file is managed by diligent commands. Manual edits are
     supported but must preserve the H2 + fenced YAML structure. -->
